content.text:
Task:
Label customer emails into one of four categories: Billing, Bug, Feature, or Other.

Output JSON:
{"category": "<one_of>", "reason": "<short explanation>"}

Examples:
Email: "I was double charged this month."
→ {
  "category": "Billing",
  "reason": "The email is about incorrect charging."
}

Email: "The app crashes when I click Export."
→ {
  "category": "Bug",
  "reason": "A specific feature is crashing."
}

Email: "Can you add a Google Sheets export option?"
→ {
  "category": "Feature",
  "reason": "User is requesting a new capability."
}

Now label this email:
"Can you add a dark mode option to the settings page?"
